{"title":"Manejo_Ventilador_Mecanico_iPad","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/UCI-Medicina Crítica/Manejo_Ventilador_Mecanico_iPad.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Manejo del Ventilador\\NMecanico y Parametros","guid":"GrIfvGvnBCkQMG49FdQ10w","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Conceptos\\NFundamentales","guid":"I8AyJiQqvBl4lq9pd2L6kQ","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"Ventilacion con presion positiva → opuesta a fisiologia normal (presion negativa)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"NO es terapia → es soporte temporal mientras se resuelve la causa","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"Descubrimiento mas importante → VM DANA los pulmones (y otros organos)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"1","text":"Estrategia LESSER IS BETTER → unica que tiene sentido en tecnica tan antifisiologica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"1","text":"Determinar el problema → trastorno de OXIGENACION vs VENTILACION","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"7","parent":"0","text":"Parametros\\NIniciales","guid":"ZDugaT_TT7Avc7H5amH3PQ","children":[{"id":"8","parent":"7","text":"Modo\\NVentilatorio","guid":"Q2NepgGewTBUNOKYfuxTEg","children":[{"id":"9","parent":"8","text":"Asisto-Control (A/C) →\\Nmodo mas usado\\Ninicialmente","guid":"RRO47nM0Mw5is61NHoWfSg","children":[{"id":"10","parent":"9","text":"Volumen Control (VCV) → volumen constante, presion variable","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"9","text":"Presion Control (PCV) → presion constante, volumen variable","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"12","parent":"8","text":"SIMV → menos usado, mayor trabajo respiratorio","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"8","text":"PSV → solo para respiracion espontanea, no soporte completo","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"14","parent":"7","text":"Volumen\\NCorriente\\N(Vt)","guid":"Znd_ORKKv-MPv3UzfSRqpQ","children":[{"id":"15","parent":"14","text":"META → 6-8 mL/kg de PESO PREDICHO (no peso real)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"14","text":"Peso predicho hombres → 50 + 2.3 x (talla pulgadas - 60)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"14","text":"Peso predicho mujeres → 45.5 + 2.3 x (talla pulgadas - 60)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"14","text":"Protocolo ARDSNet → iniciar 8 mL/kg, reducir 1 mL/kg cada 2h hasta 6 mL/kg","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"14","text":"Vt alto (>10 mL/kg) → VILI incluso sin SDRA previo (Gajic 2004)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"20","parent":"7","text":"Frecuencia\\NRespiratoria\\N(FR)","guid":"BIEtNiO1Ij9S_nWWHzNM8g","children":[{"id":"21","parent":"20","text":"Inicial → ajustar para lograr volumen minuto pre-ventilador","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"20","text":"NO exceder 35/min","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"20","text":"En obstructivos → REDUCIR\\Ndrasticamente (<10 rpm)","guid":"D5wmaWMu49M1B4LFcJYU9A","children":[{"id":"24","parent":"23","text":"Maniobra MAS potente para desatrapar aire","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"23","text":"Maximizar Te >4 seg","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"26","parent":"7","text":"FiO2","guid":"","children":[{"id":"27","parent":"26","text":"Inicial → 100% (protocolo ARDSNet)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"26","text":"Reducir precozmente → toxicidad O2 >60% prolongado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"26","text":"Meta → PaO2 55-80 mmHg o SpO2 88-95%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"26","text":"Tabla ARDSNet FiO2/PEEP para ajuste sistematico","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"31","parent":"7","text":"PEEP","guid":"","children":[{"id":"32","parent":"31","text":"PEEP bajo (5-7 cmH2O) → estandar en ventilacion protectora","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"31","text":"Funcion → stent para prevenir colapso espiratorio final","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"31","text":"En SDRA → titulacion segun tabla ARDSNet FiO2/PEEP","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"31","text":"En obstructivos → PEEP extrinseco ~80% del auto-PEEP medido","guid":"","children":[{"id":"36","parent":"35","text":"Efecto stent neumatico → facilita trigger","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"37","parent":"31","text":"PEEP NO indicado en enfermedad localizada (neumonia focal)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"38","parent":"37","text":"Presion va preferentemente a pulmones sanos → sobredistension","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"39","parent":"31","text":"PEEP alto sin mejorar PaO2/FiO2 → probable ausencia de pulmones reclutables","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"40","parent":"7","text":"Flujo Inspiratorio","guid":"","children":[{"id":"41","parent":"40","text":"Minimo 60 L/min en volumen control","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"40","text":"Debe ser al menos 2x flujo espiratorio","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"40","text":"Ajustar para mantener relacion I:E adecuada","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"44","parent":"7","text":"Relacion I:E","guid":"","children":[{"id":"45","parent":"44","text":"Normal → 1:2 o mayor","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"44","text":"En obstructivos → 1:4 a 1:5","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"44","text":"Invertida (IRV) → 2:1, solo en SDRA refractario","guid":"","children":[{"id":"48","parent":"47","text":"RIESGO → auto-PEEP y caida de gasto cardiaco","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"49","parent":"7","text":"Trigger (Sensibilidad)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"50","parent":"49","text":"Por presion → -1 a -3 cmH2O","guid":"","children":[{"id":"51","parent":"50","text":"Con PEEP alto → esfuerzo real = trigger + PEEP","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"52","parent":"49","text":"Por flujo → 2-3 L/min (MENOR trabajo respiratorio)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"49","text":"Trigger por flujo PREFERIDO → reduce trabajo del diafragma","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"54","parent":"0","text":"Modos Ventilatorios","guid":"","children":[{"id":"55","parent":"54","text":"Volumen Control (VCV)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"56","parent":"55","text":"Flujo constante durante inspiracion → onda cuadrada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"55","text":"Volumen garantizado independiente de mecanica pulmonar","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"55","text":"Presion pico VARIABLE → aumenta con resistencia o baja compliance","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"55","text":"Desventaja → presiones altas si mecanica empeora","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"60","parent":"54","text":"Presion Control (PCV)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"61","parent":"60","text":"Presion constante → flujo desacelerante","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"60","text":"Patron desacelerante → reduce presion pico y mejora intercambio gaseoso","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"60","text":"Desventaja PRINCIPAL → Vt varia con mecanica pulmonar","guid":"","children":[{"id":"64","parent":"63","text":"Si compliance baja → Vt cae","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"63","text":"Si resistencia sube → Vt cae","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"66","parent":"60","text":"Ideal en enfermedades neuromusculares (mecanica normal)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"67","parent":"54","text":"Ventilacion con Relacion Invertida (IRV)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"68","parent":"67","text":"PCV + tiempo inspiratorio prolongado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"67","text":"I:E de 2:1","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"67","text":"Previene colapso alveolar","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"67","text":"RIESGO → hiperinflacion, auto-PEEP, caida gasto cardiaco","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"67","text":"Indicacion → SDRA con hipoxemia o hipercapnia refractaria","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"73","parent":"54","text":"Presion de Soporte (PSV)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"74","parent":"73","text":"Paciente determina Vt y duracion del ciclo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"73","text":"Presion preseleccionada (5-10 cmH2O habitual)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"73","text":"Termina cuando flujo inspiratorio cae <25% del pico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"73","text":"NO proporciona soporte ventilatorio completo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"73","text":"Uso → augmentar respiracion espontanea","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"79","parent":"54","text":"SIMV (Ventilacion Mandatoria Intermitente Sincronizada)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"80","parent":"79","text":"Combina respiraciones mandatorias con espontaneas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"79","text":"MAYOR trabajo respiratorio que A/C → no recomendado como principal","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"82","parent":"0","text":"Presiones del Sistema","guid":"","children":[{"id":"83","parent":"82","text":"Presion Pico (Ppeak)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"84","parent":"83","text":"Refleja resistencia TOTAL (via aerea + pulmon + pared)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"85","parent":"83","text":"Aumenta con → broncoespasmo, secreciones, tubo acodado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"83","text":"No refleja directamente presion alveolar","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"87","parent":"82","text":"Presion Meseta (Pplateau)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"88","parent":"87","text":"Medida con pausa inspiratoria 0.5-0.8 seg (ESTANDARIZAR)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"87","text":"Refleja PRESION ALVEOLAR al final de inspiracion","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"90","parent":"87","text":"META → <30 cmH2O","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"91","parent":"87","text":"Si >30 → riesgo VILI significativo","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"92","parent":"82","text":"Driving Pressure (DP)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"93","parent":"92","text":"DP = Pplateau - PEEP","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"92","text":"META → <15 cmH2O","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"92","text":"PREDICTOR CLAVE de mortalidad en SDRA (Amato 2015)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"96","parent":"92","text":"Variable aislada MAS importante para reducir mortalidad","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"97","parent":"82","text":"Delta Pico - Plateau","guid":"","children":[{"id":"98","parent":"97","text":"Normal → <5 cmH2O","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"99","parent":"97","text":"Si >5 → aumento resistencia via aerea","guid":"","children":[{"id":"100","parent":"99","text":"Tubo acodado, secreciones, broncoespasmo","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"101","parent":"82","text":"Presion Transpulmonar","guid":"","children":[{"id":"102","parent":"101","text":"Requiere presion esofagica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"103","parent":"101","text":"Diferencia presion pulmonar de presion pared toracica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"101","text":"Util en obesos y patologia pared toracica","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"105","parent":"82","text":"Auto-PEEP (PEEP intrinseco)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"106","parent":"105","text":"Medir con pausa espiratoria","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"105","text":"Indica atrapamiento aereo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"108","parent":"105","text":"Causa → asma, EPOC, FR alta, Te corto","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"109","parent":"105","text":"Puede subestimar el problema (no mide unidades cerradas)","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"110","parent":"0","text":"Monitoreo Grafico (ABC)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"111","parent":"110","text":"Curva Flujo-Tiempo","guid":"","children":[{"id":"112","parent":"111","text":"Onda cuadrada → modo volumen","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"113","parent":"111","text":"Onda desacelerante → modo presion","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"114","parent":"111","text":"Pico flujo espiratorio → proporcional al inspiratorio (3ra ley Newton)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"115","parent":"111","text":"ANGULO ESPIRATORIO","guid":"","children":[{"id":"116","parent":"115","text":"Normal → <45 grados","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"117","parent":"115","text":">45 grados → obstruccion/resistencia aumentada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"118","parent":"115","text":"Evaluar respuesta a broncodilatadores","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"119","parent":"111","text":"Flujo que no llega a cero → AUTO-PEEP (atrapamiento aereo)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"120","parent":"110","text":"Curva Presion-Tiempo","guid":"","children":[{"id":"121","parent":"120","text":"Indice de Estres","guid":"","children":[{"id":"122","parent":"121","text":"= 1 (perpendicular) → NORMAL","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"121","text":">1 (convexa) → SOBREDISTENSION → bajar Vt o presion","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"124","parent":"121","text":"<1 (concava) → reclutamiento ciclico/colapso → subir PEEP","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"125","parent":"120","text":"5 presiones a evaluar → PEEP, pendiente, Pico, Delta Pico-Plato, DP","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"126","parent":"110","text":"Bucles Presion-Volumen","guid":"","children":[{"id":"127","parent":"126","text":"Punto inflexion inferior → nivel ideal PEEP para reclutamiento","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"128","parent":"126","text":"Punto inflexion superior → sobredistension (PICO DE LORO)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"129","parent":"128","text":"Accion → bajar Vt o presion inspiratoria","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"130","parent":"126","text":"Histeresis → refleja trabajo respiratorio y reclutabilidad","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"131","parent":"0","text":"Injuria Pulmonar (VILI y P-SILI)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"132","parent":"131","text":"Mecanismo → mecanotransduccion (fuerza mecanica → respuesta biologica)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"133","parent":"131","text":"ERGOTRAUMA → carga de energia y potencia mecanica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"134","parent":"131","text":"BAROTRAUMA → exceso de presion → ruptura alveolar","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"135","parent":"131","text":"VOLUTRAUMA → exceso de volumen → sobredistension","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"131","text":"ATELECTRAUMA → apertura/cierre ciclico → inflamacion","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"131","text":"BIOTRAUMA → respuesta inflamatoria sistemica → FOM","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"131","text":"P-SILI → injuria autoinfligida por esfuerzo excesivo del paciente","guid":"","children":[{"id":"139","parent":"138","text":"No dejar en espontaneo con alto trabajo >2-4h","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"140","parent":"131","text":"Poder Mecanico (Mechanical Power)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"141","parent":"140","text":"META → <12 Joules","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"140","text":"Integra todos los componentes de energia entregada al pulmon","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"143","parent":"140","text":">12 J → alto riesgo VILI","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"144","parent":"0","text":"Proteccion Diafragmatica","guid":"","children":[{"id":"145","parent":"144","text":"Diafragma → 70% del trabajo ventilatorio","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"144","text":"NUNCA descansa (musculo involuntario controlado por tronco)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"144","text":"Drive ventilatorio → aumentado 3-4x en falla respiratoria aguda","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"148","parent":"144","text":"Miotrauma","guid":"","children":[{"id":"149","parent":"148","text":"Carga concentrica excesiva → fatiga, proteolisis, dano miofibrillas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"150","parent":"148","text":"Carga excentrica (elongacion) → sobreasistencia, atrofia por desuso","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"151","parent":"144","text":"Monitoreo → ecografia diafragmatica (grosor y excursion)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"152","parent":"0","text":"Ventilacion Protectora","guid":"","children":[{"id":"153","parent":"152","text":"Vt 6 mL/kg peso predicho","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"154","parent":"152","text":"Pplateau <30 cmH2O","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"155","parent":"152","text":"Driving Pressure <15 cmH2O","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"156","parent":"152","text":"PEEP 5-10 cmH2O (titulacion en SDRA)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"157","parent":"152","text":"Mechanical Power <12 J","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"158","parent":"152","text":"Hipercapnia permisiva → tolerar si pH >7.20-7.25","guid":"","children":[{"id":"159","parent":"158","text":"Segura primeros 2-3 dias (antiinflamatoria)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"160","parent":"158","text":"Peligrosa >5 dias (inmunosupresion)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"161","parent":"152","text":"Si pH <7.25 → intervenir (cambiar estrategia o ECCO2R)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"162","parent":"0","text":"Asincronias Paciente-Ventilador","guid":"","children":[{"id":"163","parent":"162","text":"80-85% son asincronias de TRIGGER","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"164","parent":"162","text":"Trigger (disparo)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"165","parent":"164","text":"Esfuerzos ineficaces, auto-PEEP, debilidad","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"166","parent":"164","text":"Ajustar sensibilidad, reducir auto-PEEP","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"167","parent":"162","text":"Flujo (presurizacion)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"168","parent":"167","text":"Hambre de flujo → insuficiente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"169","parent":"167","text":"Overshoot → excesivo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"170","parent":"167","text":"Ajustar Rise Time o flujo pico","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"171","parent":"162","text":"Ciclado (terminacion)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"172","parent":"171","text":"Prematuro → doble disparo → aumentar Ti","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"173","parent":"171","text":"Tardio → esfuerzo activo al exhalar → reducir Ti","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"174","parent":"171","text":"Ajustar % ciclado espiratorio (ETS)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"175","parent":"162","text":"Espiratoria","guid":"","children":[{"id":"176","parent":"175","text":"PEEPlosis, oscilaciones post-exhalacion","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"177","parent":"175","text":"Revisar circuito, fugas","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"178","parent":"0","text":"PEEP Avanzado","guid":"","children":[{"id":"179","parent":"178","text":"Reclutamiento pulmonar","guid":"","children":[{"id":"180","parent":"179","text":"Volumen reclutable varia 2-25% del total en SDRA","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"181","parent":"179","text":"Si hay reclutamiento → PEEP mejora PaO2/FiO2","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"182","parent":"179","text":"Si NO hay reclutamiento → PEEP sobredistiende → VILI","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"183","parent":"178","text":"Efecto hemodinamico","guid":"","children":[{"id":"184","parent":"183","text":"Reduce retorno venoso → cae precarga","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"185","parent":"183","text":"Reduce compliance ventricular","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"186","parent":"183","text":"Aumenta impedancia VD","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"187","parent":"183","text":"Constriccion extrinseca por hiperinflacion","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"188","parent":"183","text":"PROMINENTE en hipovolemia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"189","parent":"183","text":"Puede mejorar GC al reducir postcarga VI (significancia incierta)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"190","parent":"178","text":"Transporte de O2","guid":"","children":[{"id":"191","parent":"190","text":"PEEP puede mejorar SaO2 pero si cae GC → DO2 NO mejora","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"192","parent":"190","text":"DO2 = GC x CaO2","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"193","parent":"190","text":"Mejorar PaO2/FiO2 sin vigilar GC es error frecuente","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"194","parent":"0","text":"Consideraciones Geriatricas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"195","parent":"194","text":"Compliance toracica disminuida → pared toracica rigida","guid":"","children":[{"id":"196","parent":"195","text":"Puede requerir presiones mas altas → vigilar transpulmonar","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"197","parent":"194","text":"Sarcopenia diafragmatica → mayor riesgo miotrauma","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"198","parent":"194","text":"Fragilidad (CFS >=5) → considerar proporcionalidad de VM","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"199","parent":"194","text":"Farmacocinetica alterada para sedacion","guid":"","children":[{"id":"200","parent":"199","text":"Dexmedetomidina PRIMERA LINEA (menos delirium)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"201","parent":"199","text":"EVITAR benzodiazepinas","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"202","parent":"194","text":"Delirium asociado a VM → CAM-ICU diario","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"203","parent":"194","text":"Weaning precoz → prevenir deterioro funcional","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"204","parent":"194","text":"Comunicacion → limitacion esfuerzo terapeutico si corresponde","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"205","parent":"194","text":"Objetivos realistas → mortalidad UCI >65a aumenta con fragilidad","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"206","parent":"0","text":"Perlas Clinicas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"207","parent":"206","text":"Driving Pressure es REY → <15 cmH2O, predictor mortalidad aislado mas importante","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"208","parent":"206","text":"Pausa inspiratoria ESTANDARIZAR → 0.5-0.8 seg, si no la medicion no es comparable","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"209","parent":"206","text":"Mechanical Power >12 J → estas danando el pulmon","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"210","parent":"206","text":"Signo del PICO DE LORO → sobredistension en bucle P-V → bajar Vt","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"211","parent":"206","text":"Angulo espiratorio >45 grados → evaluar respuesta a broncodilatadores sin auscultar","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"212","parent":"206","text":"No dejar espontaneo con alto trabajo >24h → P-SILI","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"213","parent":"206","text":"PEEP en EPOC → 80% del auto-PEEP como stent neumatico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"214","parent":"206","text":"CO2 como INOTROPICO → hipercapnia moderada aumenta GC 10-15%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"215","parent":"206","text":"Hipercapnia permisiva segura si pH >7.25, peligrosa >5 dias","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"216","parent":"206","text":"Bajar FR en obstructivos → maniobra MAS potente para desatrapar (no subir flujo)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"217","parent":"206","text":"En AM critico → dexmedetomidina sobre BZD SIEMPRE","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"218","parent":"206","text":"CAM-ICU diario en TODO paciente UCI >65a en VM","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"219","parent":"206","text":"Evaluar proporcionalidad terapeutica ANTES de intubar adulto mayor fragil","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"220","parent":"0","text":"Referencias","guid":"","children":[{"id":"221","parent":"220","text":"1. Marino P. The ICU Book. 3rd ed. Lippincott Williams and Wilkins; 2007. Cap 24-25.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"222","parent":"220","text":"2. ARDS Network. Ventilation with lower tidal volumes. N Engl J Med. 2000;342:1301-8.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"223","parent":"220","text":"3. Amato MB, et al. Driving pressure and survival in ARDS. N Engl J Med. 2015;372:747-55.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"224","parent":"220","text":"4. Devlin JW, et al. Clinical Practice Guidelines for Pain, Agitation/Sedation, Delirium. Crit Care Med. 2018;46(9):e825-73.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"225","parent":"220","text":"5. Gajic O, et al. VILI in patients without ALI at onset of MV. Crit Care Med. 2004;32:1817-24.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"226","parent":"220","text":"6. Frias A. Monitoreo de Ventilacion Mecanica (Conferencia). 2026.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"227","parent":"220","text":"7. Duenas C. Hipercapnia en Ventilacion Mecanica (Conferencia Magistral). 2026.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"228","parent":"220","text":"8. Tobin MJ. Advances in mechanical ventilation. N Engl J Med. 2001;344:1986-96.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"229","parent":"220","text":"9. Goligher EC, et al. Diaphragm dysfunction in MV. Am J Respir Crit Care Med. 2018;197:1427-31.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":229,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"UCI/Medicina Crítica","folder":"Entidades clínicas/UCI-Medicina Crítica","filename":"Manejo_Ventilador_Mecanico_iPad","id":"map_2327","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"Manejo_Ventilador_Mecanico_iPad"}